# vim-smart-gq
Redefine the gq operator to use language-specific external autoformat program

This plugin replaces the gq operator for supported filetypes by a custom version that will send the selected text to an external parser (autopep8 for python) and replace the output in the buffer.

Example usage:
  gqap - Autoformat paragraph
  gqq  - Autoformat line
  V..gq - Autoformat visual selection
  gggqG - Autoformat whole file
  
Supported filetypes:
  - Python - requires autopep8 package
  ... Feel free to add your own filetypes
  
  
